{
  "texts": [
    "This search, focusing on the terms \"ChatGPT\" and \"pathology\" returned 175 published manuscripts, showcasing the rapidly growing interest and application of LLMs within the field of pathology.",
    "Several studies and reviews have explored the integration of ChatGPT in diagnostic human pathology.",
    "ChatGPT facilitates the effective utilization and integration of knowledge that surpasses human limits and boundaries.",
    "A recent study shows that ChatGPT can generate case report templates in medical education and refining these reports under the supervision of professional educators holds considerable practical significance (6).",
    "Upon receiving a medical image, GPT-4 can initially analyze the visual features of the image, including the shape, size, structure, and morphology."
  ]
}